{
  "texts": [
    "Particularly, for each subagent, we train a specific LoRA (Hu et al., 2022).",
    "Group Planning.",
    "At inference time, once the tool name α m t generated by the PLAN-AGENT is triggered at time t, the TOOL-AGENT is roused to decide the parameters α p t transferred to the specific tool.",
    "The return result of the tool is treated as the observation o t and handed to the PLAN-AGENT.",
    "After the collaboration between the PLAN-AGENT and TOOL-AGENT reaches a prediction, the REFLECT-AGENT comes to reflect on the history and provide a reflection result contained in the reflection action α r."
  ]
}